Citizen TV news anchor Lillian Muli on Thursday made her first public appearance with Shabana FC boss Jared Nevaton as she celebrated her 35th birthday.According to sources, the two lovebirds, who have been trying to keep their relationship under wraps, would occasionally whisper sweet nothings into each other&rsquo;s ears before giggling.It's the first time that Nevaton and Muli have been seen in public together after Muli posted photos of herself posing with the city businessman and captioned them &ldquo;Bae&rdquo;.However, she deleted them later.Among those who attended her birthday bash, which was held at a posh city hotel, were Kirigo Ng&rsquo;arua, Janet Mbugua, Eddie Ndichu, Anne Kiguta and Jaque Maribe.